Package test

Class ControllerTest

java.lang.Object
test.ControllerTest
public class ControllerTest extends Object
This is a class for testing the controller in isolation. This tests the commands of the controller. This will test move, pickitem, lookaround, add human and computer player. Also display information about space and player.
